com.sri.ai.util.rangeoperation.core

Class AbstractRange<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sri.ai.util.rangeoperation.core.AbstractRange<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NullaryFunction<java.util.Iterator<T>>, Range<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DiscreteRange, GeometricIntegerRange, IntegerRange

    @Beta
public abstract class AbstractRange<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Range<T>
    Provides basic Range functionality, only leaving to the user the task of defining NullaryFunction.apply(), which should provide a new iterator over a range of values.
    Author:
    braz
